      "message": "How does code using the JGit library pass in the CredentialsProvider here?\n\nJGit has no support yet for git credential helpers (c.f. [1]), so normally for HTTPS or SSH with password code using JGit has to pass in a credentials provider. I think SSH with public key authentication would work if configured right via ~/.ssh/config.\n\n[1] https://github.com/eclipse-egit/egit/issues/191",
